<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="and-conj">and <strong><em>conj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ənd/    美 /ənd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>和；又；而：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Drive slowly and carefully.
小心，慢点儿开车。(表示并列)</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Come and give me a hand with this.
过来帮我一下。(表示目的)</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He fell and cut his knee.
他跌倒了，划破了膝盖。(表示结果)</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m feeling better and better.
我感觉越来越好。(表示程度)</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He kept on talking and talking.
他不停地说啊说。(表示反复)</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(只要…) 就：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Work hard and you’ll pass the exam.
只要用功，你就能通过考试。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Find ways to praise your children often, and you'll ﬁnd they will open their hearts to you.
想办法经常表扬你的孩子，你就会发现他们会对你敞开心扉。</p><footer>2011 山东</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>When I studied chemistry in high school, I reconsidered my goal or decided to be a doctor.   （2019 全国改错）  </li>
<li>Give me a chance,<strong><em>_</em></strong>_ I’ll give you a wonderful surprise.  （2014 天津改）  </li>
<li>The artist was born poor, <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ poor he remained all his life.   （2008 重庆）<br />
A.and<br />
B.or<br />
C.but<br />
D.so  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. or→and  2. and  3. A  </p></div>